							<title xml:lang="he">תפלות </title>
							<note>
								<p>Two pieces for the liturgy of the 9th of Av: 1. the Hafṭarah of the 9th of Av (Jer. 8:13-9:23), accompanied by an Arabic homiletical commentary taken from the midrashim; 2. the story of Ḥanah and her seven children, in Arabic verse (occupying the last eight columns of the scroll). </p>
